data.description: This super nice 3 bedroom 2 bath Ranch Style home is in a GREAT location. Just freshened up with NEW Exterior Paint, custom built Wooden Shutters, NEW ROOF, NEW AC UNIT and NEW FRONT WINDOWS! The family room and bonus room are just off the kitchen and feature a beautiful brick, wood burning fireplace. Not to mention the front and back yard oasis that includes a sprinkler system, beautiful producing Japanese plum, kumquat trees and a THRIVING GRAPEVINE! This is a very special home that is move in ready or it can be taken to the next level with your personal touch!
